				\begin{document}$$\begin{aligned} H_{joint}=-\sum _{i=0}^{n}\sum _{j=0}^{n}p(i,j)\log (p(i,j)), \end{aligned}$$\end{document}where p(i, j) is the probability of entities i and j occurring together.

